I am writing to notify the Commission of a potential exposure of personal data on a public-facing service that appears to be operated by a Philippine entity. I am an independent security researcher with {{ researcher.org or "the OSINT community" }}, and this notification is offered in the spirit of supporting compliance with the Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA 10173).

